      <title>德意志交易所遭欧盟衍生品卡特尔调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/deutsche-boerse-raided-in-eu-derivatives-cartel-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志交易所表示，该公司遭到欧盟反垄断监管机构的突击检查，监管机构怀疑该公司可能参与了与“金融衍生品”相关的卡特尔组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/deutsche-boerse-raided-in-eu-derivatives-cartel-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 08:59:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国港口罢工迫在眉睫，马士基股价上涨，运费上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/maersk-shares-jump-as-us-port-strike-looms-boosting-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场预期与美国港口工人的劳资谈判将失败，并引发新一轮的供应链中断，从而推高运费，马士基航运股价延续近期涨势，一度上涨 4.9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/maersk-shares-jump-as-us-port-strike-looms-boosting-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 08:54:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国商业信心在最新衰退警告中下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/german-business-confidence-dips-in-latest-recession-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业前景再次恶化——加剧了人们对欧洲最大经济体陷入衰退且短期内不会快速反弹的担忧。]]></description>
